---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CtaStrip from '../components/CtaStrip.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About JetAvenue: Mobile Private Jet Maintenance Experts"
  description="200+ years of combined aviation experience. JetAvenue's FAA-certified technicians travel to your aircraft for line maintenance, interior repair, and avionics support, nationwide."
  canonicalPath="/about"
>

  <section class="about-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">WHO WE ARE</p>
    <h1>Maintenance That Comes to You</h1>
    <p>JetAvenue brings FAA-certified technicians directly to your aircraft, at your FBO, home base, or wherever you're parked. No ferry flights. No repositioning. Just expert service on your schedule.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats bar -->
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">200+</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Years Combined Experience</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-div"></div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">4</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Service Disciplines</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-div"></div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">5</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Airframe Families Supported</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-div"></div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">2</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Base Locations + Nationwide</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-container">
      <div class="about-split">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p class="eyebrow">OUR MISSION</p>
          <h2>Built Around Aircraft Uptime</h2>
          <p>Private jet operators can't afford downtime. Every hour an aircraft sits waiting for a maintenance team to arrive is an hour it isn't flying. JetAvenue was built to solve that: a fully mobile maintenance operation that eliminates the logistics problem entirely.</p>
          <p>Our technicians travel to the aircraft. We coordinate with your flight department or directly with you, assess the work on-site, and execute. Whether it's a routine line check, a cabin interior repair, an avionics issue, or a post-flight detail, we handle it where the aircraft lives.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-callout">
          <blockquote>
            "Professional, quality, reliable services, delivered to your aircraft on your timeline."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Capabilities -->
  <section class="about-section about-section--alt">
    <div class="about-container">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center">WHAT WE DO</p>
      <h2 style="text-align:center">Four Service Disciplines</h2>
      <div class="cap-grid">
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-num">01</div>
          <h3>Line & Scheduled Maintenance</h3>
          <p>RON checks, MEL clearing, schedule MX, engine borescopes (Tay 611, BR700, PW800, 36-150 APUs), Pitot Static 91.411/91.413 checks, and aircraft systems troubleshooting. Part 65 privileges. Hangar access at VNY, LGB, and SDL.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-num">02</div>
          <h3>Mobile Interior Repair</h3>
          <p>Leather repair and dye, woodwork, panel recovering, carpet repair, curtain and sewing work, honeycomb panel repairs, mirror replacements, lav touch-ups, and seat/table/window shade troubleshooting, all performed on-site.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-num">03</div>
          <h3>Avionics Support</h3>
          <p>Troubleshoot, diagnose, and routine maintenance on Nav Aids, CMS systems, QAR/FDR downloads, and Pitot Static systems. 91.411 and 91.413 checks performed by certified technicians.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cap-card">
          <div class="cap-num">04</div>
          <h3>Interior Cleaning & Detailing</h3>
          <p>Interior and exterior cleaning at all levels, leather conditioning, carpet extraction, and coordinated post-maintenance cleaning. Scheduled with the MX team so the aircraft is ready when you are.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Locations -->
  <section class="about-section about-section--alt">
    <div class="about-container">
      <div class="loc-split">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">WHERE WE OPERATE</p>
          <h2>Based in LA and Arizona.<br />Available Anywhere.</h2>
          <p>Our primary bases are Van Nuys Airport (VNY) in Los Angeles and Scottsdale Airport (SDL) in Arizona. From there, our technicians travel to wherever your aircraft is parked, across the country, on short notice.</p>
          <p>If your aircraft operates outside our base markets, call us. We assess each request individually and dispatch accordingly.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="about-cta">Request a Free Assessment →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="loc-cards">
          <div class="loc-card">
            <span class="loc-iata">VNY</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Van Nuys Airport</strong>
              <span>Los Angeles, California</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="loc-card">
            <span class="loc-iata">SDL</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Scottsdale Airport</strong>
              <span>Scottsdale, Arizona</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="loc-card">
            <span class="loc-iata">&#8594;</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Nationwide</strong>
              <span>We travel to your aircraft</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaStrip />

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .about-hero {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--color-brand); text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 12px;
  }
  .about-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-ink); margin: 0 0 16px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .about-hero p {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-body);
    max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Stats bar */
  .stats-bar {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0;
    background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 32px var(--space-md);
  }
  .stat { text-align: center; padding: 12px 40px; }
  .stat-num {
    display: block; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-brand); line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    display: block; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-body); margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .stat-div { width: 1px; height: 48px; background: var(--color-border); }

  /* Sections */
  .about-section { padding: 80px 0; }
  .about-section--alt { background: var(--color-surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .about-container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--space-md); }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-ink); margin: 8px 0 24px; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .about-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  /* Mission split */
  .about-split {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: center;
  }
  @media (min-width: 860px) {
    .about-split { grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; }
  }
  .about-callout {
    background: var(--color-surface); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-brand);
    border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0; padding: 32px 28px;
  }
  .about-callout blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-ink); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  /* Capabilities grid */
  .cap-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 24px; margin-top: 40px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 700px) { .cap-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

  .cap-card {
    background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 3px; padding: 28px 24px;
  }
  .cap-num {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--color-brand); margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .cap-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-ink); margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  .cap-card p {
    font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;
  }

  /* Locations */
  .loc-split {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; align-items: start;
  }
  @media (min-width: 860px) { .loc-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }

  .loc-cards { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
  .loc-card {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px;
    background: #fff; border: 1.5px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 3px; padding: 18px 20px;
  }
  .loc-iata {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-brand); min-width: 48px; text-align: center;
  }
  .loc-card strong {
    display: block; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .loc-card span {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-body);
  }

  .about-cta {
    display: inline-block; margin-top: 24px; padding: 12px 28px;
    background: var(--color-brand); color: #fff; border-radius: 3px;
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-decoration: none; transition: background 0.18s;
  }
  .about-cta:hover { background: var(--color-brand-dark); }


  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .stat { padding: 12px 20px; }
    .stat-div { display: none; }
  }
</style>
